# Learn Python 3 the Joe Way
A modern, hands-on companion to learning Python through repetition, reflection, and real-world examples.

This project began as my personal notes while working through the classic *Learn Python the Hard Way*. 
Over time, it evolved into a structured, modern Python 3 learning system with:

- Clean Python 3 versions of each exercise  
- Concept breakdowns  
- Modern Python 3 notes  
- Alternate examples  
- Mini-challenges  
- Reflections for future learning  

